        {
            "id": "unit-wd-01",
            "title": "Module 1: HTML & CSS",
            "order": 1,
            "slides": [
                {
                    "id": "wd-s01",
                    "order": 1,
                    "type": "html",
                    "title": "Welcome to Web Development",
                    "content": {
                        "html": "<h2>Welcome to Web Development!</h2><p>The web is built on three core technologies:</p><ul><li><strong>HTML</strong> — Structure &amp; Content</li><li><strong>CSS</strong> — Styling &amp; Layout</li><li><strong>JavaScript</strong> — Interactivity &amp; Logic</li></ul><p>By the end of this course you will be able to build fully functioning web pages from scratch.</p>",
                        "layout": "default"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "id": "wd-s02",
                    "order": 2,
                    "type": "html",
                    "title": "HTML Structure",
                    "content": {
                        "html": "<h2>HTML Document Structure</h2><pre style=\"background:#f3f4f6;padding:1rem;border-radius:6px;font-size:.85rem\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\\n&lt;html&gt;\\n  &lt;head&gt;\\n    &lt;title&gt;My Page&lt;/title&gt;\\n  &lt;/head&gt;\\n  &lt;body&gt;\\n    &lt;h1&gt;Hello World&lt;/h1&gt;\\n    &lt;p&gt;My first paragraph.&lt;/p&gt;\\n  &lt;/body&gt;\\n&lt;/html&gt;</pre><p>Key tags: <strong>h1-h6</strong> headings, <strong>p</strong> paragraphs, <strong>a</strong> links, <strong>img</strong> images, <strong>div / span</strong> containers.</p>",
                        "layout": "default"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "id": "wd-s03",
                    "order": 3,
                    "type": "interactive",
                    "title": "CSS Concepts",
                    "content": {
                        "interaction_type": "tabs",
                        "instructions": "Click each tab to learn about CSS.",
                        "completion_condition": "all_tabs_visited",
                        "tabs": [
                            {
                                "id": "tab-css1",
                                "label": "Selectors",
                                "html": "<h3>CSS Selectors</h3><ul><li><code>p { }</code> — selects all paragraphs</li><li><code>.class { }</code> — class selector</li><li><code>#id { }</code> — ID selector</li></ul>"
                            },
                            {
                                "id": "tab-css2",
                                "label": "Box Model",
                                "html": "<h3>The Box Model</h3><p>Every element is a box: <strong>content → padding → border → margin</strong>. Use <code>box-sizing: border-box</code> for predictable sizing."
                            },
                            {
                                "id": "tab-css3",
                                "label": "Flexbox",
                                "html": "<h3>Flexbox Layout</h3><p>Use <code>display: flex</code> to create flexible layouts. Key properties: <code>justify-content</code>, <code>align-items</code>, <code>flex-wrap</code>, <code>gap</code>."
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
